To tap tempo in Pro Tools do these things:






Turn off the conductor track

[[File:Pro tools 8 turn off conductor .png]]






Turn off the keyboard focus




[[File:Pro tools 8 disabled key commands focus.png]]
 	                   
                         





To tap tempo, select the tempo in the transport so that it's highlighted.

Push play on the transport and then begin tapping the letter '''T''' on the keyboard in quarter notes.



[[File:Pro Tools 8 tempo selected on transport.png]]




